{"rendered": {"description": {"raw": "The [SDF spec](http://sdformat.org/spec?ver=1.6&elem=sensor#sensor_update_rate) considers an unspecified update rate to be zero and that means the sensor is updated at every cycle (i.e. as fast as possible).\r\n\r\nWithout this PR, ign-sensors was dividing by zero for unspecified rates :boom:\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nAlso added a quick fix for GPU lidars to work. Since `GpuLidar::Load` calls `Lidar::Load`, the `Lidar` class should accept `GPU_LIDAR` as a valid sensor type.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nAlso made `Sensor::SetParent` virtual, otherwise `Lidar::SetParent` was not being called on `ign-gazebo`.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>The <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://sdformat.org/spec?ver=1.6&amp;elem=sensor#sensor_update_rate\" rel=\"nofollow\">SDF spec</a> considers an unspecified update rate to be zero and that means the sensor is updated at every cycle (i.e. as fast as possible).</p>\n<p>Without this PR, ign-sensors was dividing by zero for unspecified rates <img class=\"emoji\" src=\"data/pf-emoji-service--cdn.us-east-1.prod.public.atl-paas.net/standard/551c9814-1d37-4573-819d-afab3afeaf32/48x48/1f4a5.png\" alt=\"\ud83d\udca5\" title=\":boom:\" data-emoji-short-name=\":boom:\" /></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Also added a quick fix for GPU lidars to work. Since <code>GpuLidar::Load</code> calls <code>Lidar::Load</code>, the <code>Lidar</code> class should accept <code>GPU_LIDAR</code> as a valid sensor type.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Also made <code>Sensor::SetParent</code> virtual, otherwise <code>Lidar::SetParent</code> was not being called on <code>ign-gazebo</code>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "title": {"raw": "[Blueprint] Zero update rate", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>[Blueprint] Zero update rate</p>", "type": "rendered"}}, "type": "pullrequest", "description": "The [SDF spec](http://sdformat.org/spec?ver=1.6&elem=sensor#sensor_update_rate) considers an unspecified update rate to be zero and that means the sensor is updated at every cycle (i.e. as fast as possible).\r\n\r\nWithout this PR, ign-sensors was dividing by zero for unspecified rates :boom:\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nAlso added a quick fix for GPU lidars to work. Since `GpuLidar::Load` calls `Lidar::Load`, the `Lidar` class should accept `GPU_LIDAR` as a valid sensor type.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nAlso made `Sensor::SetParent` virtual, otherwise `Lidar::SetParent` was not being called on `ign-gazebo`.", "links": {"decline": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66/decline"}, "diffstat": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/diffstat/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors:3644a9edf4a0%0D63fb1034c5f1?from_pullrequest_id=66"}, "commits": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66/commits.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66.json"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66/comments_page=1.json"}, "merge": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66/merge"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pull-requests/66"}, "activity": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66/activity.json"}, "diff": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors:3644a9edf4a0%0D63fb1034c5f1?from_pullrequest_id=66"}, "approve": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66/approve"}, "statuses": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/pullrequests/66/statuses_page=1.json"}}, "title": "[Blueprint] Zero update rate", "close_source_branch": true, "reviewers": [], "id": 66, "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "63fb1034c5f1", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-sensors/commit/63fb1034c5f1.jso